473
00:32:04,750 --> 00:32:08,245
Your children will follow your example.

474
00:32:08,875 --> 00:32:12,383
Your father is right, so pay attention.

475
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:14,050
Yes!

476
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:18,925
And Don.

477
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,491
Yes.

478
00:32:21,900 --> 00:32:24,700
I told you not to act like a loser.

479
00:32:26,220 --> 00:32:30,950
Why would you get involved in women's business and get treated like a loser?

480
00:32:31,725 --> 00:32:34,300
It wouldn't have happened if it weren't for you.

481
00:32:36,475 --> 00:32:39,525
You're their uncle, so try to set an example.

482
00:32:40,575 --> 00:32:43,025
You're younger, but you're still their uncle!

483
00:32:43,025 --> 00:32:45,325
